---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="description" content="Astro description" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-100">
		<div class="bg-white h-16 flex items-center ">
			<header class="flex justify-between container max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<h1> <span class="font-bold text-blue-500">H.</span><span>Phone</span></h1>
				<menu>
					<ul>
						<li class="inline mx-5"><a class="text-blue-600 border-b-2 border-blue-600 border-dotted"href="#">Home</a></li>
						<li class="inline mx-5"><a href="#">Shop</a></li>
						<li class="inline mx-5"><a href="#">Product</a></li>
						<li class="inline mx-5"><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
						<li class="inline mx-5"><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
					</ul>
				</menu>
				<div class="flex space-x-4">
					<Icon class="h-6 w-6" name="mdi:shopping-cart-outline" />
					<Icon class="h-6 w-6" name="mdi:search" />
					<Icon class="h-6 w-6" name="mdi:account" />
				</div>
			</header>
		</div>
		<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md shadow-slate-200 mt-6 max-w-6xl container mx-auto p-5">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 mt-10">
				<div class=" h-64 w-64 mx-auto bg-center bg-[length:110%_110%] bg-[url(https://tiendasishop.com/media/catalog/product/m/m/mme73.jpeg?optimize=high&bg-color=255,255,255&fit=bounds&height=700&width=700&canvas=700:700)]">
				</div>
				<div>
					<span class=" font-semibold text-sm bg-slate-100 rounded-full px-2 py-1">New</span>
					<h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl my-2">Apple AirPods</h1>
					<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to to-blue-300 text-white text-xl rounded-lg p-2 my-2 inline-block">3rd Generetion</span>
					<div class="flex mt-2	">
						<span class="bg-slate-100 w-3 rounded-full inline-block mr-2"></span>
						<p class="text-sm ">Portaba la corona de los Centinelas de la Noche, y los que probaron su espada le llamaron... Asesino de la Muerte.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="shadow-lg shadow-slate-200 h-12 flex justify-between items-center px-6
			">
				<div class="text-sm ">
					<span class="text-blue-500 font-semibold ">wireless Earbuds </span><span class="text-slate-400">with ligthning charging Case Spacial Audio</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex space-x-2">
					<Icon class="h-6 w-6 bg-slate-200 rounded-sm" name="mdi:chevron-left" />
					<Icon class="h-6 w-6 bg-slate-200 rounded-sm" name="mdi:chevron-right" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-12 container mx-auto max-w-6xl grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 p-4">
			<div class="bg-white shadow-md shadow-slate-300 rounded-lg p-4">
				<div class="bg-center bg-[length:100%_100%] bg-[url(https://mac-center.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-4814081_10baf2b7-1a80-4970-b191-34fb1f6f8821_823x.jpg?v=1709568183)] h-48 w-36 mx-auto mb-2"></div>
				<p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-slate-100 text-center py-1 rounded-lg">texto</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white shadow-md shadow-slate-300 rounded-lg p-4">
				<div class="bg-center bg-[length:100%_100%] bg-[url(https://mac-center.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-4814081_10baf2b7-1a80-4970-b191-34fb1f6f8821_823x.jpg?v=1709568183)] h-48 w-36 mx-auto mb-2"></div>
				<p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-slate-100 text-center py-1 rounded-lg">texto</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white shadow-md shadow-slate-300 rounded-lg p-4">
				<div class="bg-center bg-[length:100%_100%] bg-[url(https://mac-center.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-4814081_10baf2b7-1a80-4970-b191-34fb1f6f8821_823x.jpg?v=1709568183)] h-48 w-36 mx-auto mb-2"></div>
				<p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-slate-100 text-center py-1 rounded-lg">texto</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white shadow-md shadow-slate-300 rounded-lg p-4">
				<div class="bg-center bg-[length:100%_100%] bg-[url(https://mac-center.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG-4814081_10baf2b7-1a80-4970-b191-34fb1f6f8821_823x.jpg?v=1709568183)] h-48 w-36 mx-auto mb-2"></div>
				<p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold bg-slate-100 text-center py-1 rounded-lg">texto</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class=" text-2xl text-center font-semibold">
			<span class="text-blue-600">Newest</span><span class=""> Product</span>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center text-gray-600">
			A hearing aid is an electronic device worn inside or behind the ear. Amplifies certain sounds
		</div>
		<div class="bg-white h-14 flex items-center mt-10">
			<footer class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				Apple Inc. 2024
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
